    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Aprilioni qui vixit <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>enses</ex></expan> XI <lb n="3"/>et dies VII <lb n="4"/>et Inno<lb break="no" n="5"/>centiae qui <note>sic</note> vixit an<lb break="no" n="6"/>nos VII et dies XXXXVIII <lb n="7"/>Verinius Friattius <lb n="8"/>miles et Apra <lb n="9"/>fili<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> dulcissi<lb break="no" n="10"/>mis curavit faciun<lb break="no" n="11"/>dum
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Zeichnung in CIL 13, 08324 suggeriert einen Wechsel des Inschriftfeldes nach Z. 1, der am Original jedoch nicht vorliegt.</p>
            </div>
